section.p:
Create an index on node 172.23.130.24, then move it to
                node
                172.23.130.25.CREATE INDEX idx_sched1 ON `travel-sample`(attr1) 
WITH {"nodes": ["172.23.120.24:8091"]}

ALTER INDEX `travel-sample`.idx_sched1 
WITH {"action":"move","nodes": ["172.23.120.25:8091"]}

Create an index on node 172.23.120.24 with
                replicas on nodes 172.23.120.25 and 172.23.120.26, then move the
                replicas to nodes 172.23.120.27 and 172.23.120.28.CREATE INDEX idx_sched3 ON `travel-sample`(attr3) 
WITH {"nodes": ["172.23.120.24:8091", "172.23.120.25:8091", "172.23.120.26:8091"}

ALTER INDEX `travel-sample`.idx_sched3
WITH {"action":"move","nodes": ["127.0.0.24:8091", "172.23.120.27:8091", "172.23.120.28:8091"}
